data.description: Welcome to the Ridge at Canyon Springs!   This home is located in the heart of Stone Oak with an excellent school district and shopping nearby. This home offers a well groomed exterior with a blend of brick and stone and well maintained shrubs. The interior sets a classic setting as soon as you step into the entry of the home. The open layout and large windows allows for an ample amount of natural lighting into the home. The kitchen is very spacious for family gatherings and entertaining with upgraded stainless steel appliances and brand new refrigerator included with touchscreen display , from there take the entertainment to the backyard where the patio deck is within a reasonable amount of space to fit 8-10 people. The loft area upstairs is perfect for movie night or to allow the kids to turn it into a game room. Welcome Home!
